text: Tony Stewart Unplugged with Danielle Trotta - Pt. 1 OCT 01, 6:51 pm After announcing that he'll retire from Sprint Cup racing after the 2016 season, Tony Stewart sits down for an unplugged conversation with NASCAR Race Hub's Danielle Trotta.
